<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Welcome Email</title>
  <style>
    /* Add some basic CSS styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Welcome, {{name}}!</h1>
  <p>
    We're glad you've joined {{company}}! Here are some things you might find useful:
  </p>
  <ul>
    {{#each resources}}
    <li>
      <a href="{{this.url}}">{{this.name}}</a>
    </li>
    {{/each}}
  </ul>
  <p>
    If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at any time.
  </p>
  <p>Best,</p>
  <p>The {{company}} Team</p>
</body>
</html>